[size=3]  She is wanderer of Tamriel.  When she arrived and stayed High Hrothgar, Meet Dragonborn and, fascinated his Thu'um.
  She want to make a History with you.

  Race : Nord
  Weight : 100
  Height : 0.98
  Voice : Female Condescending 
  Class : Spell sword(Use Dual sword)
  Spell : Fast Healing (Self)
  Perks
  Dual flurry
  Dual savagery
  Restoration expert
  Wind walker
  Light foot
  Agile defender

  She using Leather armor set with steel swords frost and shock enchanted.

  Thanks TheWorldOfRipX
  [youtube]kBVpojVuwDc[/youtube]
[/size]
